    "body" : "<p>Quite simple:</p>\n\n<pre><code>new File(\"/Path/To/File/or/Directory\").exists();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And if you want to be certain it is a directory:</p>\n\n<pre><code>File f = new File(\"/Path/To/File/or/Directory\");\nif (f.exists() &amp;&amp; f.isDirectory()) {\n   ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
