    "body" : "<p>You need to transform your Path into a <code>File</code> and test for existence:</p>\n\n<pre><code>for(Path entry: stream){\n  if(entry.toFile().exists()){\n    log.info(\"working on file \" + entry.getFileName());\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
