    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Using <code>java.nio.file.Files</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Path path = ...;\n\nif (Files.exists(path)) {\n    // ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can optionally pass this method <code>LinkOption</code> values:</p>\n\n<pre><code>if (Files.exists(path, LinkOption.NOFOLLOW_LINKS)) {\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>There's also a method <code>notExists</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>if (Files.notExists(path)) {\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
