    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There is no need to separately call the <code>exists()</code> method, as <code>isDirectory()</code> implicitly checks whether the directory exists or not.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 158029,
      "reputation" : 22475,
      "user_id" : 376366,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 87,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/619901c6c7c16ca6a0eaf2eccc22196c?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Fernando Correia",
